				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>喺誰幣灘隔離&amp;le1就有共閒馬戲團#不如咁&amp;aa1你有冇見到暖燕瀑布&amp;aa3#暖燕瀑布下面#再右少少就會係共閒馬戲團個位&amp;laak3</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
				</ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
			</ANNOTATION>
		<ANNOTATION>
			<ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a3" TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts7" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts10">
